!! Relationship to Darwin
Dawkins' work is a refinement of Darwinian natural selection. While Darwin focused on the survival of the individual, the "Selfish Gene" perspective explains ''why'' certain individuals survive: they possess the genes most effective at building successful survival machines.

!! Individual vs. Gene
* Darwinism: Focus on the ''Phenotype'' (the visible trait).
* The Selfish Gene: Focus on the ''Genotype'' (the underlying code).